metadata.name: BURNING OF THE SOUL
metadata.description:
The burning of the soul from love is a fire that never goes out. 
It is the feeling when the heart beats harder, when every cell of the body is ready to accept love and give it back in return. 
It is the warmth that envelops everything around us and makes the world brighter and more beautiful. 
It is the feeling that makes us fight for our love and never let it go. 

The burning of the soul from love is the truest magic that can happen in everyone's life.

Acrylic on the canvas 
Art size 2352x3609px
